NAME
    System::Introspector - framework for remote system introspection

SYNOPSIS
      $ system-introspector --storage <path> --config <path> [OPTIONS]

    See system-introspector(1) for detailed information about which OPTIONS
    can be used.

DESCRIPTION
    System::Introspector is a framework for remotely executing system wide
    introspection. The introspection is done executing a set of probes on
    the remote system that gather specific information. Gathered results are
    stored in JSON format.

